8
00:01:44,001 --> 00:01:45,085
No luck.

9
00:01:45,127 --> 00:01:46,587
Do it the other way.

10
00:01:46,628 --> 00:01:48,005
I tried that too!

11
00:01:48,130 --> 00:01:52,301
Fuck, then we can't get WhatsApp?

12
00:01:52,426 --> 00:01:53,302
Nothing.

13
00:01:54,219 --> 00:01:56,096
Hey, Kim Ki-taek.

14
00:01:56,930 --> 00:02:00,100
Don't fucking pretend to sleep.
What do you think?

15
00:02:00,934 --> 00:02:06,690
Our phones are shut off.
Now our wi-fi is shut off.

16
00:02:07,274 --> 00:02:10,319
What's your plan?

17
00:02:12,780 --> 00:02:14,114
- Ki-woo.
- Yes, Dad?

18
00:02:14,281 --> 00:02:17,826
For wi-fi, hold it high.

19
00:02:19,286 --> 00:02:23,040
Stick it in every corner
and so on.

20
00:02:26,877 --> 00:02:30,631
Damn stink bugs.

21
00:02:31,548 --> 00:02:33,634
