22
00:02:33,801 --> 00:02:35,219
Really? You got a signal?

23
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,929
Yeah, see?

24
00:02:37,179 --> 00:02:39,640
This one,
'coffeeland 2G'.

25
00:02:39,890 --> 00:02:41,725
Did a new cafe open?

26
00:02:41,975 --> 00:02:43,560
Why can't I get it?

27
00:02:43,685 --> 00:02:45,270
Climb up here.

28
00:02:45,395 --> 00:02:46,355
Hey kids.

29
00:02:47,481 --> 00:02:48,148
Does it work?

30
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,066
Yeah.

31
00:02:49,191 --> 00:02:51,443
Then check WhatsApp.

32
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:54,279
Pizza Generation
said they'd contact me.

33
00:02:54,905 --> 00:02:56,240
Hold on.

34
00:02:56,907 --> 00:02:59,076
Here it is.
Pizza Generation.

35
00:03:02,412 --> 00:03:05,874
Wow!
Check this out, guys.

36
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:09,461
If we go as fast as her,
we can finish today.

37
00:03:09,628 --> 00:03:10,879
Then we can get paid.

38
00:03:10,921 --> 00:03:14,091
- Should we stand up too?
- She's a pro.

39
00:03:14,591 --> 00:03:17,177
What? Fumigation?

40
00:03:19,221 --> 00:03:20,681
They still do that kind of thing?

41
00:03:20,806 --> 00:03:21,765
Guess so.

42
00:03:21,849 --> 00:03:22,599
Shut the window.

43
00:03:22,724 --> 00:03:25,185
Leave it open.
We'll get free extermination.

44
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,687
Kill the stink bugs.

45
00:03:27,104 --> 00:03:29,606
Right, too many
stink bugs these days...

46
00:03:32,025 --> 00:03:34,069
God, that smells!

47
00:03:36,822 --> 00:03:38,407
I told you to shut it!

48
00:03:38,740 --> 00:03:40,492
Should I shut it, Dad?

49
00:03:51,378 --> 00:03:53,130
What exactly is the problem?

50
00:03:54,381 --> 00:03:57,217
Take this one as an example.

51
00:03:57,467 --> 00:03:59,428
