52
00:04:00,053 --> 00:04:01,930
And why's it folded here?

53
00:04:02,264 --> 00:04:03,640
Why is this sticking up?

54
00:04:04,057 --> 00:04:06,435
You didn't even fold it.

55
00:04:07,561 --> 00:04:11,315
